hadiths.en:
In the narration of Al -Sakuni from Imam Jafar ibn Mu hammad Al -Sadiq {a.s} 
from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir {a.s}, it is reported:  
"Indeed, Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib {a.s} crucified a man in Al -Hirah for three days. Then on 
the fourth day, Imam {a.s} took him down, prayed over him, and buried him." 
[REFERENCES] Man La Yahduruhu Al-Faqih, Vol.4 p.68  
﴿HADITH ﴾
